iller_Getty-Images-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>所有幸存的成员，RZA，GZA，Raekwon，Ghost Faceface Killah，Method Man，Inspectah Deck，U-God和Masta Killa都将在那里</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wu-tang-clan-announce-the-final-chamber-last-ever-tour-with-north-american-dates-with-run-the-jewels-3840886">Wu-tang氏族邮报宣布，“最后的会议厅”上一次巡回演出与北美约会与Run The Jewels一起</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="RZA（顶部）和（L-R）U-God，Raekwon，Masta Killa和Wu-Tang Clan的Cappadonna表演。信用-Ethan Miller/Getty Images" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/RZA-top-and-L-R-U-God-Raekwon-Masta-Killa-and-Cappadonna-of-Wu-Tang-Clan-performing.-Credit-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">Wu-Tang氏族</a>宣布了他们的最后一场巡回演出“ Wu-Tang Forever：The Final Chamber”的开始，并在北美约会，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/run-the-jewels">获得了夏季珠宝</a>的支持。</p><p>工作人员今天（2月24日）在社交媒体上宣布了新闻，并在2025年6月和7月在奥斯汀，坦帕，波士顿，芝加哥，芝加哥，底特律和纽约等城市列出了日期清单。运行珠宝将参加所有宣布的日期。</p><p>所有幸存的成员 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rza">RZA</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gzagenius">GZA</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raekwon">RAEKWON</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghostface-killah">GHOSTFACE KILLAH</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/method-man">Method Man</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inspectah-deck">Inspectah Deck</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u-god">U-God</a>和Masta Killa  - 定于“ Wu-Tang Forever：The Final Chamber”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGddQ5DsQv3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1