ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Sam-Fender">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a>的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">《 People Watch》（People Watch）</a>正朝着第一名的位置，目前已经超出了英国前十名中的其余组合。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">Sam Fender  - “观看人”评论：反光和敏锐的独立摇滚乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sam-fender-people-watching-number-1-album-midweek/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜</a>，North Shields本地人正迅速努力成为他最近发行的第三张专辑的官方第一张专辑。 2月21日发布的“观看者”在短短三天后已经获得了2025年最大的开幕周。</p><p> Fender目前正在超越前十名中的其余与专辑相结合，其中80,000台已经发生了变化。预计“观看的人”将加入他的2019年首次亮相“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">Hypersonic导弹</a>”和2021年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">十七岁</a>”作为排行榜的LP。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812392" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812392" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）“观看”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812392" class="wp-caption-text">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）“观看”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>如果Fender在开幕周内能够转移超过100,000个单位，那么他将成为第一位英国独奏艺术家，因为<a href="/artists/Harry-Styles">Harry Styles</a>于2022年与“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-new-album-harrys-house-3226209">Harry&#39;s House</a> ”这样做。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019"><em>NME</em>在对“观看者”的四星级评论中，</a>将LP描述为“来自北盾的闪亮之星的反光和敏锐的独立岩石”。</p><p>它读到：“由于他的名声迅速升起，英国吉他英雄将其迅速升起，使他的旧工人阶级生活感到存在，连根拔起和脱节。”</p><p>前十名中的其他行为正在与第一名作斗争，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tate-mcrae">泰特·麦克雷（Tate McRae）</a> <a href="/artists/partynextdoor">，</a><a href="/artists/drake">其中</a>包括“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-so-close-to-what-review-3840099">如此近的东西</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">”</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-all-the-artists-drake-mmentioned-on-some-sexy-songs-4-u-3838134">Carpenter</a>其他的。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）的最糟糕的旅行习惯和新专辑进度|英国奖2022" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/neP8XRRvDaw?start=114&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed"