9?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsam-fender-tickets%2Fartist%2F5242347" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">在此处</a>找到英国巡回演出的清单。</p><p>他还在下个月的仪式上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">获得了两项英国颁奖典礼的提名</a>：年度艺术家和Alt/Rock Act，并已宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announced-as-record-store-day-uk-official-ambassador-3834386">2025年Record Store Day的正式大使。</a>该活动将于4月12日举行，Fender将发布。两首新歌曲作为特殊EP庆祝的一部分。</p><p>最重要的是，最近宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-raye-and-more-to-headline-2025-f1-british-grand-prix-3839703">Fender将是今年一级方程式英国大奖赛的头条新闻之一。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-currently-outselling-rest-of-uk-top-10-combined-people-watching-3840843">萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）目前卖出了英国十大前十名，总共是“观看人”的头号，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
