键指控”，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-on-the-deeper-meaning-of-not-like-us-it-is-the-type-of-man-i-represent-3804972">针对肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的diss曲目对他的释放，“不像我们”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dj-khaled-receives-rip-drake-coffin-delivery-3840783">DJ Khaled帖子收到“ Rip Drake”棺材的交付，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
