screen></iframe></p><p>在首次露面时，她揭开了新的女子北美冠军腰带，并帮助杰冯·埃文斯（Je&#39;von Evans）和特里克·威廉姆斯（Trick Williams）赢得了一场标签队。第二次，雷德（Red）主持了高级现场活动<em>战场</em>，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-teaches-wrestling-legend-shawn-michaels-to-twerk-wwe-nxt-battleground-3764586">摔跤传奇人物肖恩·迈克尔斯（Shawn Michaels）在后台闲逛，教了名人堂成员厅</a>。十月是她上次在<em>NXT</em>上进行的，在脚跟明星Ethan Page被切断之前，在戒指上发表演讲（或“削减促销”）。</p><p>其他说唱歌手也参与了WWE的参与，包括<a href="/artists/travis-scott">特拉维斯·斯科特（Travis Scott）</a> ，<a href="/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根（Megan Thee）种马</a>和<a href="/artists/rm">RM</a> ，他们的歌曲（分别为“ 4x4”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-and-bts-rm-announce-new-single-neva-play-3789648">“ Neva Play”</a> ）配乐WWE的其他品牌<em>Raw</em> and <em>SmackDown</em> 。 <a href="/artists/bad-bunny">Bad Bunny</a>和<a href="/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>也在平方圈中进行了战斗 - 前者曾经举行过现已失去的24/7冠军。</p><p>自从Red出现WWE以来，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruno-mars-teases-strip-club-anthem-with-sexyy-red-3831580">与Bruno Mars合作，共同为“脱衣舞俱乐部国歌”“胖，多汁和湿”</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bruno-mars-and-sexyy-red-team-up-with-lady-gaga-and-blackpinks-rose-on-raunchy-new-single-fat-juicy-wet-3831689">在随附的音乐录影带中</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">Blackpink</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rose">Rosé</a>制作了自己的客串。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="性感的红色和布鲁诺火星 - 脂肪多汁和湿（官方音乐录影带）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d7OROxsW5ZY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Red发行的最后一张唱片是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-drops-her-highly-anticipated-mixtape-in-sexyy-we-trust-drake-lil-baby-tay-keith-mike-will-made-it-3759212">去年5月的“ Sexy We Trust”</a> - 她的第三个混音带和她2023年突破性LP的后续作品《胡德的最热门公主》。这项14轨项目是由她的长期合作者Tay Keith制作的，并具有说唱重量级<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-baby">Baby</a> ，Drake，Vonoff1700和Mike-Will-Made-IT。</p><p>在巡回唱片时，Red因舞台设计而受到了反对，其中包括一顶大型充气帽，上面写着：“让美国再次Sexyy”。在去年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/questlove-defends-sexyy-red-appearing-on-roots-picnic-2024-line-up-3590902">年度扎根野餐中有争议</a>之后，该道具<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-responds-to-donald-trump-maga-hat-comparisons-make-america-sexyy-again-3762799">以错误的方式摩擦了许多方法，并认为红色认可了特朗普 - 她热切地否认了特朗普。</a></p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sexyy-red-could-have-been-a-wwe-superstar-rapping-and-wrestling-are-pretty-much-the-same-3838691">Sexyy Red could have been a WWE superstar: “Rapping and wrestling are pretty much the same”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
宠物店男孩参加伦敦乌克兰集会的演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/pet-shop-boys-to-attend-london-ukraine-rally-with-performance-from-antytila-3840830?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pet-shop-boys-to-attend-london-ukraine-rally-with-performance-from-antytilaLiberty Dunworth Mon, 24 Feb 2025 16:56:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsDonald TrumpPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3840830 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Taras Topolia of Antytila and Neil Tennant of Pet Shop Boys" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> It takes place today (February 24), on the third anniversary of the invasion</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pet-shop-boys-to-attend-london-ukraine-rally-with-performance-from-antytila-3840830">Pet Shop Boys to attend London Ukraine rally with performance from Antytila</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Taras Topolia of Antytila and Neil Tennant of Pet Shop Boys" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Antytila-Pet-Shop-Boys@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">宠物店的男孩</a>已经确认，他们将今天（2月24日）在伦敦参加乌克兰集会。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ukrainian-band-antytila-interview-front-line-army-russia-war-ed-sheeran-benefit-conert-birmingham-3192406">乌克兰乐队Antytila在福利节目之前与我们交谈：“我们试图向人们展示一些光明”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>该活动定于特拉法加广场（Trafalgar Square）举行，将于今晚6:30 PM GMT举行。 Dubbed &#39;Heart-Broken But Unbroken&#39;, it will be taking place on the third anniversary of the war on the country and is backed by a coalition of Ukrainian organisations.</p><p> “We unite, not just for ourselves, but for Ukraine&#39;s sovereignty, freedom, and future.我们的存在将是一个有力的陈述 - 不容忽视的声明。” Instagram上的描述写道。 “这不仅仅是集会；这是一份声明。 A declaration that Ukraine&#39;s voice must be heard.宣布我们将在和平与正义盛行之前我们不会休息。与乌克兰站在一起。”</p><p> It also adds that “British politicians, Ukrainian officials, and representatives from our allied nations” have offered backing, and a performance will be held by the Ukrainian band <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/antytila">Antytila</a> .</p><p>现在，宠物店的男孩在网上分享了一份新的声明，确认他们将参加集会。他们昨晚（2月23日）宣布了这一消息，在Facebook上上传了该活动的海报，并写了标题：“在那里见！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpetshopboys%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02UT333maJ4yX23BcNWVaCsHr2BbRJ25fonkSZtqqfwdXXPyrfnbYUgDEQXS2KqGDol&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="609" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>自从俄罗斯于2022年开始全面入侵乌克兰以来，成千上万的人被杀，此后三年尚未达成和平协议。 Outlets including <a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/24/g-s1-50107/ukraine-war-3-years-russia-invasion" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NPR</em></a> have recalled how the recent re-election of <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">Donald Trump</a> to US President has had an impact on the circumstances, with Russia&#39;s bargaining power seemingly rising.</p><p>特朗普上个月返回白宫后，他说他想迅速结束战争，此后，他继续与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）以及沙特阿拉伯的美国和俄罗斯代表团组织讨论。但是，有些人越来越担心美国总统倾向于找到一项支持莫斯科的决议。</p><p>欧洲领导人目前正在与乌克兰总统沃罗迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskyy）谈论结束冲突，此前总统表示愿意辞职以换取北约为他的国家的会员资格。他的评论是在战争中最大的一次无人机袭击之后，官员们说昨晚有267人进入该国（2月23日），导致伤亡。</p><p> As for the performance from Antytila at tonight&#39;s rally, the Ukrainian pop-rock band formed in 2007 and have released six studio albums.他们正计划在战争开始之前的2022年在自己的祖国进行体育场巡回演出，并在新闻发布后继续担任士兵。</p><p>那一年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ukrainian-band-antytila-share-footage-of-one-day-from-the-war-from-kyiv-3196119">他们发布了一段视频，上面有前线捕获的镜头，</a>以显示乌克兰各地看到的破坏，说：“您应该知道这一点，我们别无选择，只能捍卫我们的国家，我们会这样做直到我们得到胜利当然。”</p><p>他们还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ukrainian-band-antytila-interview-front-line-army-russia-war-ed-sheeran-benefit-conert-birmingham-3192406">从前线与<em>NME</em>进行了交谈，并解释了他们希望他们的音乐能够传来，以作为对战争挣扎的人的支持的信息</a>。 Frontman Taras Topolia said at the time: “We&#39;re not just for entertainment – we like to say something important through our music.我们试图向人们展示一些灯光，并说一切都会好起来的，即使现在看起来很难。”</p><p>他继续说：“我们试图向粉丝解释如何在黑暗时期抗拒和生活，就像我们喜欢为娱乐和跳舞写歌一样。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGNMFQmN4qU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326